Name: Jimmie Johnson's Anything With an Engine

Achievements.Name: Beginner
Achievements.Description: Complete a Career Mode event

Achievements.Name: Rookie Champ
Achievements.Description: Complete Career mode by playing all events on Rookie difficulty or higher

Achievements.Name: Pro Champ
Achievements.Description: Complete Career mode by playing all events on Pro difficulty or higher

Achievements.Name: All-Star Champ
Achievements.Description: Complete Career mode by playing all events on All-Star difficulty

Achievements.Name: Speedster
Achievements.Description: Win your first Time Attack event, in Career Mode or Single Event (Regulation rules)

Achievements.Name: Endurer
Achievements.Description: Win your first Endurance event, in Career Mode or Single Event (Regulation rules)

Achievements.Name: Duelist
Achievements.Description: Destroy an opponent's car in a Duel, in Career Mode or Single Event

Achievements.Name: Saboteur
Achievements.Description: Destroy an opponent's car as the Chicken Bomb in a Multiplayer Survival event

Achievements.Name: Traveler
Achievements.Description: Complete an online Multiplayer event

Achievements.Name: Homebody
Achievements.Description: Complete a local Multiplayer event

Achievements.Name: Tinkerer
Achievements.Description: Build a new vehicle in the Garage

Achievements.Name: Enthusiast
Achievements.Description: Complete 50 Events in Single Event mode (Regulation Rules)

Achievements.Name: Collector
Achievements.Description: Build all vehicles in the Garage

Achievements.Name: Explorer
Achievements.Description: Discover and successfully traverse an Expert Shortcut

Achievements.Name: Renegade
Achievements.Description: Discover and traverse all Expert Shortcuts successfully

Achievements.Name: Sprinter

Achievements.Name: Marathoner

Achievements.Name: Boxer

Achievements.Name: Rascal
Achievements.Description: Use every Gotcha to successfully strike at Bot opponents

Achievements.Name: Achiever
Achievements.Description: Earn all Badges in a Single Event Race (Regulation rules)

Achievements.Name: Comeback Kid!
Achievements.Description: Win a Single Event Race (Regulation rules) by climbing from last to first place in the final lap

Achievements.Name: Advocate
